result.name: forkers

reviews.text:
Quality is good with this price! The dinner set is so good but it’s a bit too much for us.. 2 starters, 2 soups (should try their signature shrimp soup), salad, french fried! 
For the main course, we love the pork so much! Juicy! 

Staffs are nice, good services.
Great restaurant hidden in to gua wan ! Amazing food quality and feel free to bring your own wine !

Forkers this one is a hidden gem in To Kwa Wan. Very good food, very exclusive, and really great people that owns this place. Bring your choice of drinks, share a glass and for sure the owners will enjoy one together with you. With great food and company this makes it the best environment to enjoy a night.
Nice food with reasonable price but waiting a little bit long tonight
